videos.description: UNC QB Mitch Trubisky scrambles out of the pocket and finds T.J. Logan who runs 22 yards and dives in to the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: UNC takes early lead with Logan 22-yard TD

videos.description: Ricky Aguayo 50 yd FG BLOCKED blocked by Jeremiah Clarke  Andre Smith return for 30 yds to the NCaro 41
videos.headline: R. Aguayo 50 yd FG blocked by Jeremiah Clarke, A. Smith return for 30 yds
Aguayo misses third FG of game

videos.description: UNC RB T.J. Logan runs 13 yards for his second touchdown of the game, increasing the Tar Heel's lead over Florida State by two scores.
videos.headline: UNC extends lead over Florida State with Logan's second TD

videos.description: UNC QB Mitch Trubisky fakes the throw before running out of the pocket and diving for the pylon, scoring a 4-yard touchdown to increase the Tar Heel's lead over Florida State by three scores.
videos.headline: Trubisky dives for pylon, extends UNC's lead by three scores

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Jesus Wilson for 36 yds to the NCaro 39 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Francois throws dime for big gain

videos.description: Florida State RB Dalvin Cook runs for a 9-yard touchdown for the Seminoles' first score of the day.
videos.headline: Cook puts Florida State on the board with 9-yard TD

videos.description: Elijah Hood run for a loss of 3 yards to the FlaSt 5 Elijah Hood fumbled, forced by Matthew Thomas, recovered by FlaSt Jacob Pugh
videos.headline: North Carolina fumbles in red zone

videos.description: Jacques Patrick runs for 19 yds for a TD after he recovers his own fumble in the end zone
videos.headline: Florida State's Jacques Patrick recovers own fumble for TD

videos.description: Mitch Trubisky pass complete to Mack Hollins for 15 yds for a TD
videos.headline: M. Trubisky pass to M. Hollins for 15 yds for a TD

videos.description: Dalvin Cook run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: D. Cook runs 1 yard for a TD

videos.description: Dalvin Cook run for 3 yds for a TD
videos.headline: Dalvin Cook 3rd rushing touchdown of the day ties the game at 28

videos.description: North Carolina WR Thomas Jackson charges down the sideline into the end zone, putting The Tar Heels up 34-28 on the Seminoles.
videos.headline: Jackson's 34-yard TD puts Tar Heels on top

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jacksons 34-yard TD puts Tar Heels on top) 2016/10/01

videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Dalvin Cook for 41 yds to the FLORIDAST 33 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: D. Francois pass,to D. Cook for 41 yds for a 1ST down,

videos.description: Ricky Aguayo makes go ahead extra point to give Florida Stae 35-34 lead
videos.headline: Ricky Aguayo makes go ahead extra point to give Florida Stae 35-34 lead

videos.description: Nick Weiler's 54-yard FG attempt is good and North Carolina wins 37-35
videos.headline: UNC wins on 54-yard field goal, trolls FSU with tomahawk chop

videos.description: North Carolina surrenders a 21-0 lead but comes out on top with a 54-yard field goal as time expires to defeat No. 12 Florida State 37-35.
videos.headline: UNC tops FSU with last-second field goal
